      "text": "Database : when deciding  pg-proimse first think of possiblities whether the row exists or not then what response does it send\nwhat response u want based on all the factors select db method\n\nbackend route handler:\n    input validation\n    response send by data : 1 row zero row or error constraints\nsends approriate resposne based on that ",
